<P>
 AND ONE MORE THING: At the recent Rose Bowl press conference and blimp landing 
ballyhooing Pink Floyd's upcoming tour, journalists asked about virtually every 
detail of the undertaking. 
</P>
<P>
 But it was left to Pop Eye to zero in on the issues that everyone really wants 
to know: Will there be a pig and will there be a wall? 
</P>
<P>
 Floyd manager Steve O'Rourke, seeming a little flustered, stared back and, 
after a pause, said merely, "I can say this: There won't be a wall." 
</P>
