<HEADLINE>
<P>
ROSTENKOWSKI PAYS UP TO SALVAGE INTEGRITY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Rep. Dan Rostenkowski (D-Ill.) repaid the House nearly $82,000 for office 
equipment, saying he would err "on the side of reimbursing the government" 
rather than have his integrity doubted. 
</P>
