routed Nevada, 99-70, to snap a seven-game Big West losing streak. The 
Anteaters (6-14, 3-9) jumped out to a 17-2 lead and rolled to the victory, 
dominating every facet of the game. Irvine had 23 more rebounds than the Wolf 
Pack (9-12, 5-8). 
