 Cerritos 6, Pierce 2 -- Justin Wildhorn pitched a complete game, scattering 
seven hits for Cerritos. He overshadowed Pierce starter Adam West (0-2), who 
allowed two earned runs and no walks in 6 2/3 innings. WOMEN'S BASKETBALL 
</P>
