 Southern Utah 85, Cal State Northridge 52 -- Cherri Shurtliff scored 22 points 
for the Thunderbirds in a nonconference game. Michelle Esparza led the Matadors 
(3-18) with 15 points. 
</P>
<P>
 UC San Diego 70, Cal Lutheran 66 -- The Regals' bid to rally from a nine-point 
halftime deficit fell short in a nonconference game at Cal Lutheran. Melissa 
Wood had 15 points for Cal Lutheran (6-13). 
</P>
<P>
 Canyons 87, Bakersfield 55 -- The Cougars clinched at least a share of the WSC 
