<DOCNO> LA021394-0313 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 013186 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 13, 1994, Sunday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
