<DOCNO> LA021394-0453 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 016541 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 13, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
